Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.34,0:00:23.33,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.33,0:00:26.65,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,I see. Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.39,0:00:32.54,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,It's the beginning of a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.92,0:00:49.02,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Why did you come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.02,0:00:53.76,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. You're the only person I know outside of the organization, Li-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.83,0:00:57.98,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea who that girl is?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.98,0:01:00.07,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Aniki told me she was some sort of merchandise.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.07,0:01:03.04,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Why did you bring her here if you already knew that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.07,0:01:08.08,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,I'm infatuated with her! I've decided to make her happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.08,0:01:09.52,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.52,0:01:12.76,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,How? Well, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.30,0:01:20.97,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,I'll find a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.29,0:01:25.16,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Why... Why are you so upset?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.88,0:01:27.49,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,What are you going to do about the organization?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.47,0:01:30.10,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,I don't have any other choice but to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.10,0:01:32.23,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,I'm sure Aniki's angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.23,0:01:35.52,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,I'm going to run away from Tokyo with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.92,0:01:38.10,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,There's no way you could pull that off.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.10,0:01:40.14,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,I won't know until I try!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.82,0:01:47.39,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,I'm an idiot who doesn't know how the world works,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.39,0:01:53.21,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,but I believe she'll never be happy if she stays here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.21,0:01:54.93,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.40,0:01:59.69,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,You don't understand anything at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.05,0:02:17.01,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Did Kenji do this to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.01,0:02:18.19,DTB-Default,Manager,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.19,0:02:20.89,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Did he run away with the doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.89,0:02:22.01,DTB-Default,Manager,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.12,0:02:26.86,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,That punk... He did this at the worst possible moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.86,0:02:27.99,DTB-Default,Gangster A,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.72,0:02:31.00,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Ask the customer to wait a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.00,0:02:34.02,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Tell him I'll think about giving him a discount depending on how things turn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.02,0:02:34.63,DTB-Default,Gangster A,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.59,0:02:39.44,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Why do you think I had the old man killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.44,0:02:44.47,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,I'm more concerned about how many officials I can extort before the turmoil subsides.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.47,0:02:46.31,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,I need the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.31,0:02:48.13,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,If you understand what I'm saying, leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.13,0:02:48.92,DTB-Default,Gangsters,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.43,0:02:53.66,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Listen, you guys. Find them at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.66,0:02:55.41,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Don't lay a finger on the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.41,0:02:56.93,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Kill the guy if you have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.93,0:02:57.78,DTB-Default,Gangsters,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.94,0:03:06.53,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,Oh, doesn't that sweater look cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.53,0:03:09.04,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Hey, aren't you done shopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.04,0:03:11.17,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.30,0:03:19.22,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,BK201?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.86,0:03:24.03,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.03,0:03:26.18,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Slowly turn this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.81,0:03:31.18,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Li-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.10,0:03:34.38,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Oh, Kirihara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.38,0:03:36.10,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.10,0:03:37.85,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,It really has.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.85,0:03:39.34,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,How have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.37,0:03:45.21,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Um... This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.65,0:03:46.35,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,Who's he?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.78,0:03:50.49,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Um... How should I explain this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.49,0:03:51.85,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.93,0:03:58.19,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,It's okay. Say no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.19,0:04:00.28,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Hey, don't misunderstand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.38,0:04:08.30,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,I'd understand if he was buying clothes as a present for his girlfriend, but underwear and a wig?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.30,0:04:10.05,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,Are you jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.05,0:04:11.09,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,I told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.09,0:04:12.39,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.13,0:04:16.57,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,Why do you think it's a present?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.17,0:04:24.30,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Thank you for helping me with the decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.69,0:04:28.08,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Li-kun, those things weren't for you, were they?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.95,0:04:29.79,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.30,0:04:32.56,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.56,0:04:35.41,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,A friend asked me for a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.41,0:04:38.90,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,He asked me to find a present for his girlfriend
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.90,0:04:41.28,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,since he didn't have any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.64,0:04:44.03,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.03,0:04:45.93,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,O-Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.64,0:04:49.22,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.65,0:04:56.35,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,Aren't you glad it wasn't a present for his girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.35,0:04:57.19,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.19,0:05:01.94,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,Really? The way you were looking at him didn't seem normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.94,0:05:03.47,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.65,0:05:21.20,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Li-san, you're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.20,0:05:23.42,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,I do live here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.14,0:05:25.49,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.49,0:05:26.64,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,A change of clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.19,0:05:30.97,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,There's no way she'd get very far in that outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.67,0:05:32.93,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Li-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.88,0:05:35.43,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.19,0:05:41.29,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.29,0:05:43.33,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Is she your girlfriend, Li-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.33,0:05:46.03,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,She came into the room without saying a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.23,0:05:51.35,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Were you monitoring me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.15,0:05:54.47,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Huang's instructions?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.81,0:05:58.37,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.37,0:06:00.96,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Hei, you seemed a little different today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.00,0:06:03.43,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.43,0:06:04.32,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.09,0:06:06.74,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Help her change.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.14,0:06:20.31,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Are you okay with that person?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.92,0:06:27.05,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,I apologize for the trouble I'm causing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.63,0:06:29.10,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Are you serious about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.10,0:06:30.32,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.77,0:06:35.95,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Always on the run, living in fear of pursuers who might come at any moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.95,0:06:38.54,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,You're going to have to run for the rest of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:40.33,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,I'm aware of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.33,0:06:42.16,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,What about money?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.16,0:06:43.75,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Housing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.75,0:06:48.57,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Even if you're lucky enough to find a job, how are you going to take care of her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.57,0:06:50.66,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,She's not even toilet trained.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.65,0:06:53.05,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,I'll find a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:55.89,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Why her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.63,0:06:59.79,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,She doesn't understand your words or your reasoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.79,0:07:01.67,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Why are you so concerned about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.15,0:07:11.62,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:14.55,DTB-Default,Eileen,0,0,0,,Oh, you're here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.55,0:07:16.09,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,You're dressed up, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.09,0:07:18.01,DTB-Default,Eileen,0,0,0,,I'm off to work, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.01,0:07:21.08,DTB-Default,Eileen,0,0,0,,I don't sit around and drink all day, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.08,0:07:22.63,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Have a good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:30.61,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Li-san, do you know why Eileen came to Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.25,0:07:36.98,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,She's here to earn money for her brother and sister back in her homeland.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.98,0:07:42.36,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,She wasn't able to get a decent education, which is why she doesn't want her siblings to be in the same situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.18,0:07:47.09,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,That's because they're related by blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.98,0:07:52.13,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,What difference does that make? I was abandoned by my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.63,0:07:55.88,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Eileen isn't the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.88,0:08:03.00,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Louis, Joshua, and Babo... Everyone has a reason for living.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.59,0:08:05.41,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Li-san, don't you have it as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.41,0:08:08.53,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Something you want to protect from the bottom of your heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.90,0:08:14.88,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Sorry, I said a little too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.27,0:08:17.51,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,You can't help being lovestruck, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.54,0:08:28.84,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,I'll take you to the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.48,0:08:32.01,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,I'll take you to Shinjuku Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.68,0:08:33.96,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Li-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.94,0:08:39.16,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Tickets to the first express out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.16,0:08:41.17,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Any destination is fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.17,0:08:43.21,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,I need two tickets now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.21,0:08:44.08,DTB-Default,Attendant,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.98,0:08:49.42,DTB-Default,Attendant,0,0,0,,The earliest departure is an express bound for Matsumoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.42,0:08:50.92,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,I'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.92,0:08:51.51,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Kenji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.59,0:08:53.64,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.30,0:08:56.91,DTB-Default,Attendant,0,0,0,,Sir, your change!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.33,0:09:01.04,DTB-Default,Thugs,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.43,0:09:02.23,DTB-Default,Gangster A,0,0,0,,Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:05.96,DTB-Default,Gangster A,0,0,0,,You guys go after them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.96,0:09:08.07,DTB-Default,Gangster A,0,0,0,,I'm going to call Hitotsubashi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.07,0:09:09.01,DTB-Default,Thugs,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.01,0:09:14.28,DTB-Default,Announcement,0,0,0,,This is an announcement addressed to the following customer...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.10,0:09:20.10,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.65,0:09:30.15,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,You two go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.15,0:09:31.31,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,What about you, Li-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.31,0:09:32.57,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,We'll manage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.89,0:09:38.86,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Li-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.35,0:09:43.04,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Let's go, Yin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.56,0:09:47.58,Title,,0,0,0,,Episode Eighteen A Love Song Sung from a Trash Heap... (Part Two)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.18,0:09:59.86,DTB-Default,Gangster A,0,0,0,,It's only the broad?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.86,0:10:01.22,DTB-Default,Gangster A,0,0,0,,Where did the others go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.44,0:10:10.60,DTB-Default,Gangster B,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.02,0:10:13.88,DTB-Default,Gangster B,0,0,0,,Bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.81,0:10:16.32,DTB-Default,Gangster B,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.52,0:10:21.28,DTB-Default,Gangsters,0,0,0,,Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.28,0:10:21.99,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.99,0:10:24.70,DTB-Default,Gangsters,0,0,0,,{\an8}Open up! Open the door, bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.95,0:10:23.80,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.77,0:10:37.82,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Good. I think we're...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.22,0:10:51.81,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,It's dangerous to run out like that, Kenji.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.53,0:10:56.27,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,A-Aniki...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:05.20,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,If you're looking for the kid and the doll, they were caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.74,0:11:08.22,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,How long have you been watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.47,0:11:13.69,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,It's about time to pull out. The kid's going to die and the doll's going to be sold.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.69,0:11:17.65,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,When that happens, they're going to find out about your involvement.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.65,0:11:20.30,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,It'll be impossible for you to continue your mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.30,0:11:23.19,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,You guys better run away at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.94,0:11:30.39,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,If you're involved with that kid any longer, it'll be seen as betrayal against the syndicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.76,0:11:32.87,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Are you going to report this to Huang?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.87,0:11:34.31,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Give me some credit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.31,0:11:36.98,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,What would I gain out of telling him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.98,0:11:39.08,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,I'm just here to kill time,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.72,0:11:42.57,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,since you never fail to amuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.31,0:11:45.07,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.01,0:11:49.08,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Yes, since we were the ones at fault,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.08,0:11:50.97,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,I'll give you a discount.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.40,0:11:53.64,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Allow us to continue providing our services in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.96,0:11:59.03,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Shit, open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.03,0:12:00.88,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,I'll open it soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.37,0:12:04.17,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,It'll be the last thing you'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.70,0:12:06.13,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.04,0:12:13.07,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Is it the doll's observer apparition?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.10,0:12:16.49,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Is it spying on us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.49,0:12:17.63,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.91,0:12:20.04,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,She's calling us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.09,0:12:25.93,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,She's saying, "Kenji... will be killed... Save him."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.93,0:12:27.14,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.14,0:12:30.74,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Are you saying that the doll sent its observer apparition on its own?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.74,0:12:31.95,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,That's hard to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.30,0:12:35.94,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,The yakuza using the doll must have set a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.94,0:12:37.68,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,There's no other explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.09,0:12:39.46,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.46,0:12:43.70,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,You were the one who said I seemed different today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.22,0:12:45.70,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Why did you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.61,0:12:50.98,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Ask where it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.43,0:12:58.89,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Never a dull moment with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.02,0:13:04.48,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,That was stupid of you, Kenji.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.48,0:13:07.68,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,You're throwing your life away for the sake of a doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.18,0:13:11.85,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,What are you saying, Aniki?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.58,0:13:15.38,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,She isn't an object...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.38,0:13:17.29,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,She's a girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.05,0:13:20.29,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,not a doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.29,0:13:21.30,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.04,0:13:25.63,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,How long are you going to continue acting delusional?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.39,0:13:31.39,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,I've decided to risk my life for her sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.87,0:13:37.83,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,I can do anything as long as I have this will.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.57,0:13:45.26,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,I dare you to find a way out of this situation, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.83,0:13:47.16,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Aniki...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.16,0:13:49.20,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Why are you so upset?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.20,0:13:49.99,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.99,0:13:53.49,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,You're the one who said it a long time ago, Aniki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.86,0:13:56.56,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.66,0:14:10.59,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,A stun gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.26,0:14:46.42,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.42,0:14:49.73,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Aniki, stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.59,0:14:53.49,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Get into the car, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.99,0:15:06.11,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Li-san, will you have my motorbike?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.02,0:15:10.07,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Please take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.27,0:15:12.07,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.25,0:15:17.81,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Where do you want me to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.81,0:15:19.55,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Shinjuku Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.09,0:15:21.21,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.42,0:15:36.35,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,This is the second time you've sat in the back,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.75,0:15:38.18,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Yeah, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.93,0:15:41.47,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,although the last time was on a motorcycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.51,0:15:48.52,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,That was my first time on a bike,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.95,0:15:51.76,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,and it was the first time I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.29,0:15:53.62,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.14,0:16:00.70,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Listen, a motorcycle isn't just a machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.91,0:16:05.25,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,If you take good care of it, it'll listen to your wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.61,0:16:07.33,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,It'll never let you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.64,0:16:09.83,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.83,0:16:11.77,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,You probably don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.77,0:16:12.97,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.79,0:16:15.32,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.40,0:16:21.58,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Listen, kid. Find something you want to protect with your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.22,0:16:27.06,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,When you do, there isn't anything in this world you'll be afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.81,0:16:29.96,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,You'll be able to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.57,0:16:51.07,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Why did you let him go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.07,0:16:52.86,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.86,0:16:56.36,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,There wasn't any ammunition left in that gun,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.36,0:16:58.53,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,but you already knew that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.97,0:17:00.57,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,I wasn't aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.22,0:17:06.05,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.75,0:17:12.84,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Is there something you want to protect with your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.25,0:17:16.95,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,I don't have anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.23,0:17:21.97,DTB-Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,I did in the past, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.91,0:17:23.95,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.13,0:18:10.84,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,Hey... It might be a little too late to say this, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.55,0:18:14.96,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,You don't have to stay with me, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.96,0:18:20.66,DTB-Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,If you don't like me, feel free to leave whenever you want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.25,0:18:31.68,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Hitotsubashi is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.68,0:18:35.45,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,It looks like a guy named Ohshita will take over the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.45,0:18:37.69,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,What about our mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.12,0:18:41.30,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,The trafficking route ceased to exist the moment Hitotsubashi was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.30,0:18:43.01,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Our mission has been canceled.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.44,0:18:44.77,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.06,0:18:47.51,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Hei?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.06,0:18:49.89,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.83,0:18:59.17,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,There was a response from BK201?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.17,0:19:02.11,DTB-Default,Mayu,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, but it was really faint.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.11,0:19:03.39,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Time and location?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.93,0:19:07.04,DTB-Default,Mayu,0,0,0,,Several minutes, starting from 19:12 last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.04,0:19:10.93,DTB-Default,Mayu,0,0,0,,The exact location hasn't been confirmed, but it was probably Shinjuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.14,0:19:14.30,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,He was in the vicinity after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.42,0:19:18.27,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Was there any other news worth mentioning during that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.27,0:19:20.34,DTB-Default,Mayu,0,0,0,,It occurred a little later,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.34,0:19:25.33,DTB-Default,Mayu,0,0,0,,but there was a shooting incident at Shinjuku Station's south exit, believed to be part of a gang war.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.33,0:19:27.41,DTB-Default,Mayu,0,0,0,,A mob official was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.41,0:19:28.72,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Shooting incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.16,0:19:30.45,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.45,0:19:32.94,DTB-Default,Mayu,0,0,0,,Nothing else has been reported.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.50,0:19:34.71,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.53,0:19:37.67,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,All right. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.19,0:19:45.74,DTB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,When will you make your next appearance, BK201?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.77,0:19:49.18,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.57,0:19:52.49,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Sorry for all the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.49,0:19:56.34,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it. It's part of my job as a landlord.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.96,0:19:58.31,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Kiritanpo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.69,0:20:02.42,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,Don't you know what that is? It's an Akita dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.42,0:20:04.95,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,Is that boy in Akita?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.02,0:20:06.76,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.76,0:20:09.60,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,This is a lot for one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.60,0:20:12.58,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,I think he wanted to share this with everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.53,0:20:17.90,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Can you distribute it to everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.26,0:20:21.74,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,What are you saying? Hand it out yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.79,0:20:27.20,DTB-Default,Landlady,0,0,0,,What's with that face? That's common courtesy, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.52,0:20:48.50,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,The faces of those who are gone float beyond the bubble that glitters of gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.32,0:20:52.92,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,The woman who lost her memory serves a smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.38,0:20:57.13,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,The man who lost his love drinks a glass of despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.51,0:21:02.47,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,His unabated indignity won't melt away,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.47,0:21:04.45,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,so he continues to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.26,0:21:07.75,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,However, he cannot get drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.26,0:21:09.26,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,538)}Episode Nineteen Dreaming Shallow, Uninebriated... (Part One)